smartContracts.name: Thala CDP / Lending (vault_scripts)
smartContracts.description: Thala collateralized lending and borrowing; user entry points are in vault_scripts (deposit_collateral, withdraw_collateral, borrow, repay). No lending module on-chain.

extensions.receiptTypeNote: CDP position (vault::Vault); no transferable receipt token.

smartContracts.name: Thala Lending (IL alias)
smartContracts.description: IL uses lending::deposit/withdraw/borrow/repay; on-chain entry points are vault_scripts (deposit_collateral, etc.). This alias matches IL module name so SCL/IL param audit resolves. Payload args: u64 amount, vector<address> collateral types (64-char hex).

extensions.receiptTypeNote: IL alias; actual entry points in vault_scripts (deposit_collateral, withdraw_collateral, borrow, repay).
